shall live ♪

10:50.150 --> 10:53.740
♪ Hey, Venus ♪

10:53.740 --> 10:56.320
♪ Oh, Venus ♪

10:56.320 --> 10:59.280
♪ Make my wish come true ♪

10:59.280 --> 11:03.360
♪ Make my wish
come true ♪

11:03.360 --> 11:05.360
♪ Make my wish come true. ♪

11:08.420 --> 11:09.500
