13:47.660 --> 13:49.750
♪ Rockin' robin ♪
Yeah.

13:49.750 --> 13:51.250
♪ Rockin' robin ♪
Blow it, Rich!

13:53.250 --> 13:54.250
♪ Hey, rockin' robin ♪

13:54.250 --> 13:56.540
♪ 'Cause you're really gonna
