14:10.720 --> 14:12.800
Yowza, yowza, yowza,

14:13.300 --> 14:16.310
and Jill's challenge jitterbug
really took its toll.

14:16.310 --> 14:18.940
Four more couples
have dropped out.

14:18.940 --> 14:21.640
Well, we're gonna take
a two-minute break right now.

14:21.640 --> 14:23.230
Now everybody remember,

14:23.230 --> 14:25.230
they got to be back
on the dance floor

